Product Name: Fantech REVOLVER GP12 Gaming Controller Gamepad Joystick USB
Customer Review: Barang sampai dengan aman walau pengiriman antar pulau. Review 3 hari pemakaian: kualitas yang ngagetin dengan range harga segini, apalagi saya beli saat diskon 43%. Tombolnya tinggi, tactile, analognya responsif dan sensitif, L-R3-nya clicky, trigger dan bumper enak dipencet, linear triggernya juga beneran fungsi, ga cuma embel-embel nama, rumble atau getarnya juga fitur tambahan yang bagus. build qualitynya terasa premium, ga kopong, dengan body yang doff finish jadi enak dipegang, kabelnya juga braided. Tapi layoutnya yang lumayan lebar, agak sulit buat yang tangannya kecil, dan D-pad-nya sayangnya juga bukan yang terbaik buat jempol lu kelamaan pake, karna pinggirannya yang tajem sama bentuknya yang salib jadi rada renggang di bagian serong, jempol lu bakal terasa sakit kalo terusan geser-geser mencet D-pad-nya, apalagi saya priNegativei yang pakai controller ini buat main game gelut. Walau gitu saya ga nyesel beli ini, untuk range harganya, kualitasnya tetep ngangetin, setara dengan controller konsol ori. Recommended product.
Customer Review English: The goods arrived safely even when shipping between islands. Review after 3 days of use: surprising quality at this price range, especially when I bought it at a 43% discount. The buttons are tall, tactile, the analogue is responsive and sensitive, the L-R3 is clicky, the trigger and bumper are easy to squeeze, the linear trigger is also really functional, it's not just a name, rumble or vibration, it's also a good additional feature. The build quality feels premium, it's not hollow, the body has a matte finish so it's nice to hold, the cable is also braided. But the layout is quite wide, a bit difficult for those with small hands, and unfortunately the D-pad is also not the best for your thumbs if you use it for a long time, because the sharp edges and the cross shape become a bit loose at an angle, your thumbs will feel sore. If you keep moving around pressing the D-pad, what's more, I'm a negative person who uses this controller to play wrestling games. Even so, I don't regret buying this, for the price range, the quality is still impressive, on par with an original console controller. Recommended product.
